      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for a fantastic project opportunity! This vehicle is in poor condition and will require some dedicated mechanical and cosmetic attention to get it back to its best, but it's the perfect choice for a DIY enthusiast or someone looking for a budget-friendly way to get started. It\u2019s priced to sell and ready for its next chapter with a owner who isn't afraid of a little hard work!",
