      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle is preserved in pristine condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from the day it left the showroom. Meticulously maintained and subject to a rigorous multi-point inspection, it represents the pinnacle of pre-owned excellence. For the discerning driver who demands nothing less than absolute perfection, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity to acquire a masterpiece of engineering in its finest state.",
