    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been totally babied, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for its next big adventure, you've found it! Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it in person\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a pristine example of the S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, featuring an 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous response. Mated to a precise 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission, the drivetrain is mechanically flawless. Proactive maintenance includes upgraded rod bearings and throttle actuators, ensuring long-term reliability of the high-revving internals. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M Variable Differential Lock, providing exceptional lateral grip and torque vectoring. With zero subframe fatigue and a factory-fresh underside, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of BMW M-division engineering in showroom condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. No mechanical issues. Flawless interior and exterior. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 43500.0,
