    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a truly peerless example of automotive excellence. This vehicle has been maintained to a standard rarely seen outside of a museum, having spent its life in a climate-controlled environment and under a fitted cover. The exterior finish is breathtaking, with deep, mirror-like paint that has been treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating; there are no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections to be found. Every panel gap is factory-perfect. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary that still retains its new-car aroma. The premium leather seating surfaces show zero signs of ingress or egress wear, and the high-gloss interior trim is free of even the finest hairline scratches. All technology suites, including the premium audio and navigation systems, operate with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is indistinguishable from new. It comes with a complete, chronological binder of every service performed by authorized technicians, ensuring its performance is as sharp as its appearance. With low mileage and a spotless pedigree, this is an opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a turn-key masterpiece that requires absolutely no apologies.",
      "price": 48900.0,
